<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Grady Rueffer for CS Representative</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <img class="hero-img" src="/images/banner.jpg" alt="Grady Rueffer with McMaster University campus" />
  <div class="hero-scrim-left"></div>
  <div class="hero-scrim-bottom"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-line"></span>
        CS Representative &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; McMaster
      </div>
      <div class="hero-name">Grady <b>Rueffer</b></div>
      <div class="hero-tagline">Debug the Disconnect. Build CS Together.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#platform" class="btn-gold">See My Platform &rarr;</a>
      <div class="hero-note">Vote March 25&ndash;27 via McMaster email</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<section class="experience" id="experience">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="label"><span class="label-line"></span>Experience You Can Count On</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">I Know How to Show Up for Students</h2>
    <p class="section-body">I've served as First-Year Representative for Computer Science and Student Senator in high school. I know how to get things done at the institutional level. Too many CS students don't know the opportunities in front of them, or don't believe they exist at all. That changes with me as your rep.</p>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        <div class="stat-num">2+</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Years in Student Politics</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">CS Rep + High School Senator</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        <div class="stat-num">1</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Program to Unite</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">CS: connected, not siloed</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        <div class="stat-num">&#8734;</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Open Door Policy</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">No concern too big or small</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PLATFORM -->
<section class="platform" id="platform">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="label"><span class="label-line"></span>Platform</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three Promises to CS</h2>
    <p class="section-body">Concrete commitments, not vague ideas. Here's exactly what I'll deliver as your representative.</p>
    <div class="promises">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">[ ]</div>
        <div class="card-title">Shared Spaces for Collaboration</div>
        <p class="card-body">No more hunting for a free room in the library or hatch. I'll create a system for finding and booking collaborative workspaces, plus dedicated areas where CS students can connect.</p>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Bookable collaborative workspaces</li>
          <li>Drop-in areas for solo and group work</li>
          <li>Spaces designed for CS ingenuity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">&#123;&#125;</div>
        <div class="card-title">Empower CS Clubs &amp; Initiatives</div>
        <p class="card-body">I'll streamline the process for clubs, new and existing, to apply for and receive MES funding, and advocate for software-related clubs to get the reach they deserve.</p>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Simplified club funding pipeline</li>
          <li>MES affiliation support for CS clubs</li>
          <li>Amplified reach for student initiatives</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">&lt;/&gt;</div>
        <div class="card-title">Bridge the Inter-Program Divide</div>
        <p class="card-body">CS students shouldn't feel like outsiders in the faculty. I'll create cross-program events that connect CS with all engineering disciplines and make sure our issues are heard.</p>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Cross-discipline mixer events</li>
          <li>CS-specific issues escalated to MES</li>
          <li>Accessible rep for every CS student</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
